token_info.name: Extrude in volume
token_info.description: The minimalistic objects illustrate the state of the virtual world passing through volumes. Motion vectors and abstract volumes create architectural structures of the social struggle. By Vlas Belov. Website: http://vlasbelov.tilda.ws/page16098593.html.  Created in 3D editor 2017. You can see it in AR if you visit this page from your smartphone and tap on the AR button in the lower left corner.
